# Data layer per specs/shared/system-architecture.md.
# In-memory caches over bundled JSON. ConceptRegistry, ActivityRegistry,
# RewardCatalog, FoundryCatalog, TelemetryCatalog, StandardsReference, plus
# lazy loaders for LessonRuntime, ActivityNarration, StringTable, SlotVocabulary,
# and the AssetPathResolver. All read-only at runtime.
